data.description: Lovely & beautifully maintained home with a great lay-out; open design, kitchen with breakfast bar, corner fireplace, spacious master with large master bath.  This home will welcome you as soon as you walk in, it's wide doorways and special handicap handles in bathrooms are perfect for persons with physical disabilities.  Check out the enclosed back porch, partially covered; perfect for hot summer months.  Garage has been partially converted to a study or game room, can be easily converted back to a garage.  Many more amenities!
